item.title: Executive Producer Anele Mdoda on Oscars nomination
item.description: South Africa has reason to celebrate with its first Oscar nomination in 20 years! South African film "The Last Ranger", directed by Cindy Lee, was nominated in the category of Best Live Action Short Film at the 97th Academy Awards, to be held in March 2025. Carol Ofori spoke to one of the Executive Producers Anele Mdoda. Feed: https://iono.fm/rss/chan/5916

item.title: Adventureland
item.description: How long does it take to load a saved game of Adventureland on the TRS-80? A little over a year, apparently. Kay and Carrington are back and ready to tackle tricky text adventures once again. It's a Christmas disaster! I mean, a Christmas miracle!... Feed: https://feeds.libsyn.com/91191/rss
